Introduction: ~300-400 characters

Each main section: ~300-450 characters maximum

Conclusion: ~100-200 characters

If over character limit, compress in this order:

Remove redundant phrases and filler words

Shorten bullet points to essential elements only

Condense paragraph sections while keeping key tactical details

Reduce number of examples/bullets per section if necessary

